Check status of roolout
kubectl rollout status {deployment name}

rollout
kubctl roolout undo {deployment name}


There are 2 Node update strategies
  1. ReCreate # Drop all of Nodes and create new 
  2. RollingUpdate # Drop and re-create each of Node 1 by 1

 How to set strategy
  pod > spec >strategyType=RollingUpdate|ReCreate
   